CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780510264
OL,3,CInquest into death of 'bubbly'
OL,4,Cteenager who got into difficulty in sea
OL,6,FAn inquest is due to open into the
OL,7,Fdeath of a teenage girl who died after
OL,8,Fgetting into difficulty in the sea.
OL,10,FChiedza Nyanjowa was pulled from the
OL,11,Fwater at Formby Beach by members of
OL,12,Fthe public during record-breaking warm
OL,13,Fweather on Bank Holiday Monday.
OL,15,FThe 15-year-old was rushed to Alder
OL,16,FHey Children's Hospital in a critical
OL,17,Fcondition but passed away four days
OL,18,Flater on Saturday, 30 May.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780510264
OL,3,CInquest into death of 'bubbly'
OL,4,Cteenager who got into difficulty in sea
OL,6,FHer family, who are from Cheshire,
OL,7,Fhave described her as "bubbly" and say
OL,8,Fshe will be "remembered for her kind
OL,9,Fspirit."
OL,11,FThe incident has sparked an
OL,12,Finvestigation into safety measures at
OL,13,Fthe popular beauty spot, which
OL,14,Ffrequently sees massive influxes of
OL,15,Fvisitors during warm weather.
OL,17,FSefton Central MP Bill Esterson
OL,18,Fconfirmed that a multi-agency debrief
OL,19,Fhas already taken place to look into
OL,20,Fthe events surrounding the girl's
OL,21,Fdeath.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780510264
OL,3,CInquest into death of 'bubbly'
OL,4,Cteenager who got into difficulty in sea
OL,6,FHe said: "Merseyside Police will also
OL,7,Fseek support from the Local Resilience
OL,8,FForum to ensure the best possible
OL,9,Fmeasures are in place to firstly
OL,10,Fprevent and secondly respond to
OL,11,Fsimilar incidents in future."
OL,13,FThe MP stressed that the review would
OL,14,Flook at wider, long-standing
OL,15,Finfrastructure and safety issues in
OL,16,Fthe area to prevent future coastal
OL,17,Ftragedies.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780510264
OL,3,CInquest into death of 'bubbly'
OL,4,Cteenager who got into difficulty in sea
OL,6,FHe added: "I will support these
OL,7,Freviews and work with all relevant
OL,8,Fagencies to ensure that improvements
OL,9,Fare made to protect lives and to
OL,10,Faddress the ongoing problems caused to
OL,11,Fpeople living near the beach.
OL,13,F"As such, I will be meeting
OL,14,Frepresentatives of the relevant
OL,15,Forganisations following the inquest.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780510264
OL,3,CInquest into death of 'bubbly'
OL,4,Cteenager who got into difficulty in sea
OL,6,F"I have asked my team and local
OL,7,Fcouncillors to ensure that issues
OL,8,Fincluding parking restrictions,
OL,9,Fenforcement, emergency access and
OL,10,Flonger-term interventions are a
OL,11,Fpriority at next week's meeting of the
OL,12,FFormby Stakeholders Group.
OL,14,F"I want all relevant agencies around
OL,15,Fthe table to consider what further
OL,16,Faction can be taken and how practical,
OL,17,Fsustainable solutions can be delivered
OL,18,Fto improve public safety and reduce
OL,19,Fthe risks when we have lots of
OL,20,Fvisitors.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780510264
OL,3,CInquest into death of 'bubbly'
OL,4,Cteenager who got into difficulty in sea
OL,6,F"For now, my focus is on supporting
OL,7,Four emergency services and respecting
OL,8,Fthe inquest process as it takes its
OL,9,Fcourse."
OL,11,FThe coroner's inquest is set to
OL,12,Fformally open on Wednesday, 3 June.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
